Notore Chemical Industries Plc is a leading fertilizer and agro-allied companies in Africa based in Rivers State with interests in power, chemicals and agriculture is seeking to hire a creative and resilient candidate to head our procurement and contracts unit. The ideal candidate would be expected to develop, maintain and lead a coordinated and strategic approach to procurement and contract management for the Notore Group, seeking value for money, relationship and performance management of suppliers.The role has responsibility for efficient and effective procurement of goods, services and contract management in line with corporate objective, best practices and policy.&nbsp;&nbsp; Apply at https://ngcareers.com/job/2019-06/procurement-and-contracts-manager-at-notore-chemical-industries-plc-28/ Source: NG Career